  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/946",
  "title": "Given a query, after refresh, searchBox cursor jumps at the begining of the input",
  "body": "When having `autofocus: true` in the searchBox widget and `urlSync` activated in the instantsearch, the search box is populated with the previous search query after a reload happens and the cursor is placed (with focus()?) into the search box input field.\n\n![unbenannt](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/36167/13947604/cc067efc-f01b-11e5-94b6-d9e12075d880.PNG)\n\nIn this case I would **expect that the cursor is placed at the end** of the query and not at the beginning. \n",
